TreeSitter.LanguagePack
=======================

This package bundles `language_definitions.json`, the machine-readable grammar
manifest from the tree-sitter-language-pack project:

    https://github.com/kreuzberg-dev/tree-sitter-language-pack

The manifest data (repository URLs, pinned revisions, grammar sub-directories,
C-symbol overrides, file extensions, and ambiguity hints for ~306 languages) is
used here under the terms of that project's MIT License. All credit for curating
and maintaining the manifest belongs to the tree-sitter-language-pack authors.

The individual tree-sitter grammars referenced by the manifest are owned by their
respective upstream authors and distributed under their own licenses; this package
ships only the manifest plus any locally-built grammar libraries.
